framebuffer animation driven by timer irqs. 
also implemented unified makefile

## To build

export USE_QEMU=1   # one time
or 
# export USE_QEMU=1 # one time

```
make clean
make
```

## To run

### Windows PowerShell
'C:\Program Files\qemu\qemu-system-aarch64.exe' -M raspi3 -kernel Y:\teaching\p1-kernel-workspace\p1-kernel\src\lesson03-bonus\kernel8.img -serial null -serial stdio


